                            <comment id="14654109" author="mithun" created="Tue, 4 Aug 2015 18:34:13 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The fix. The hard-codes for &lt;tt&gt;part&lt;/tt&gt; in the file-names have been switched to use the conf-setting for &lt;tt&gt;&quot;mapreduce.output.basename&quot;&lt;/tt&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Sorry for the delay.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14654111" author="mithun" created="Tue, 4 Aug 2015 18:35:15 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Causes silent failures and potential data-loss (because last-write-wins). We should patch 1.2.0.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
